  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Amerikan is an eco-friendly, mountain lodge-style hotel with easy access to the slopes. The hotel's sun terrace or the wellness area are great places to relax after a day on the slopes, make time to have a dip in the indoor pool and whirlpool for a moment of peace.</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>The hotel's location right next to the No.10 Amerikan drag lift means you can connect directly to the Carosella Gondola and be on the mountain in no time. You can ski almost all the way back to the hotel as well. If you are looking for somewhere to have a drink or bite to eat during the day, catch the free resort bus into the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno">Livigno</a>, where you can find a range of lively bars, restaurants and shops. </p>
<h2>Alpine style</h2>
<p>The hotel has a modern alpine feel to it, with bright and airy rooms and warm wood throughout the public areas of the hotel. There's a variety of rooms to choose from, whether you are after cosy and compact bedrooms with a typical alpine style, or a modern bedroom with panoramic views, there is one which will meet your needs. The Suites sleep up to six people, making them a great option for families heading to <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a> this winter.</p>
<h2>Relaxation</h2>
<p>When you return from a day skiing, the bar and sun terrace is a great spot for your post-ski hot chocolate or aperitif before dinner. Once you have soaked up some winter sun on the terrace, don't miss out on some spa time before dinner. Enjoy the massage jets in the indoor pool, relax in the jacuzzi or revitalise in the two saunas or steam room - there is also a lovely relaxation area with loungers. When it comes to meals you can enjoy typical Italian dishes and classic Valtellinese cuisine.</p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Close to lifts</strong> - With a drag lift right next to the Hotel Amerikan you can be on the slopes in no time.</p>
<p><strong>Wellness area</strong> - Chill out after a day on the mountain at the hotel's heated indoor pool, whirlpool, sauna and Turkish bath.</p>
<p><strong>Tasty food</strong> - You can look forward to breakfast and dinner here, especially traditional dishes from the region.</p>]]></description>
